title: Aaron Rodgers, Khalil Mack, Baker Mayfield, Steelers, and the Cowboys
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, Khalil Mack, Baker Mayfield, Steelers, and the Cowboys
description:
Colin explains why Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers is the real loser in the Khalil Mack trade, Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield's latest appearance on Hard Knocks, and the problems with the Pittsburgh Steelers and the Dallas Cowboys. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Bryan Cox, and Brian Westbrook.
